{"tid":2129021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎香港家下死左22個人，7月之後死既都係特區政府，陳肇始，同屌過黑醫黑護撐政府既人害既","createTime":"2020-07-28T10:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T04:28:52.000Z","uid":179775,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87d2450150c32fdbd8d534fe5bd0d22a29e86ae1","tid":2129021,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:14:22.000Z","msg":"拜幾多神作幾多福都無用<br />\n準備報應<br />\n上天會同你地計清楚嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n有貴人想幫香港<br />\n你屌走貴人<br />\n助長特區政府林鄭殺人害人<br />\n<br />\n全香港都睇住特區政府推香港人去死<br />\n而你班藍絲黑警有份係度幫佢地手<br />\n<br />\n記住呀。   死亡重未停嫁<br />\n<br />\n本來有機會阻止，但你們有份立喊助威<br />\n一個一個推去死亡"},{"pid":"56a3b7add5c8dbc34a65a9dab4765c2271f9c627","tid":2129021,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:15:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03d197ebc6802c346c24860f552a5dec04ffe740","tid":2129021,"uid":138964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"幫佢地立定個碑<br />\n<br />\n冤有頭債有主<br />\n<br />\n市民我唔理政治<br />\n<br />\n但高官用政治手段玩鳩你咁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faea434ca0c173d50e7ca6a3f0e2a247f2a263b","tid":2129021,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"其實老人院班廢老冇肺炎都就死㗎啦"},{"pid":"d924ec9bcac76cd324a95bc87fe7b79a0ef2ab76","tid":2129021,"uid":179775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03d197ebc6802c346c24860f552a5dec04ffe740","tid":2129021,"uid":138964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"幫佢地立定個碑<br />\n<br />\n冤有頭債有主<br />\n<br />\n市民我唔理政治<br />\n<br />\n但高官用政治手段玩鳩你咁啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T10:28:41.000Z","msg":"係。冤有頭債有主<br />\n<br />\n本來有班貴人想保護香港人<br />\n係班藍絲 黑警趕走貴人，黏埋溫神度<br />\n害死咁多人"},{"pid":"b206bec67085995ef9eb0646ce4632d7bf403f57","tid":2129021,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime